---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import { siSpotify, siApplemusic, siYoutubemusic } from "simple-icons/icons";
---

<Layout>
  <section class="flex flex-col gap-10 mx-auto max-w-4xl">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold">Albums</h1>
      <p class="text-lg max-w-2xl">
        Here are some of the songs I've worked on. I'm always looking for new opportunities to learn
        and grow as an artist. If you have a project in mind, feel free to reach out. 🙂
      </p>
    </div>

    <ul class="flex flex-col gap-10">
      {/* Elderly School - An ode to the human condition */}
      <li>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span>Elderly School - An ode to the human condition</span>
          <a
            href="https://open.spotify.com/track/6VmZPxlRPKH5pFLY28Ptgf?si=3073023e2eea4882"
            class="transition-colors hover:text-primary hover:drop-shadow-[0_0_6px_var(--color-primary)]"
            aria-label="Listen to Elderly School on Spotify"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="size-5 fill-current" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d={siSpotify.path}></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://music.apple.com/us/song/elderly-school/1675247384"
            class="transition-colors hover:text-primary hover:drop-shadow-[0_0_6px_var(--color-primary)]"
            aria-label="Listen to Elderly School on Apple Music"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="size-5 fill-current" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d={siApplemusic.path}></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://music.youtube.com/watch?v=HTa9Gnw39rw&si=IFcP3wezFRYwepfT"
            class="transition-colors hover:text-primary hover:drop-shadow-[0_0_6px_var(--color-primary)]"
            aria-label="Listen to Elderly School on YouTube Music"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="size-5 fill-current" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d={siYoutubemusic.path}></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </h2>
        <article class="flex flex-col md:flex-row! gap-4 pt-4">
          <figure class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
            <Image
              loading="eager"
              class="w-full h-94 aspect-square object-cover rounded-xl border"
              width={800}
              height={800}
              src="/music/posters/elderly_school.png"
              alt="Weekend at Bernie's inspired poster for the song Elderly School."
            />
            <audio controls preload="metadata" class="w-full">
              <source src="/music/songs/elderly_school.mp3" type="audio/mpeg" />
            </audio>
            Beats by CRITICAL BASS THEORY
          </figure>

          <div
            class="flex flex-col
              md:max-w-xl md:max-h-120! max-h-56
              rounded-xl border bg-muted
              p-4
              scrollbar-visible"
          >
            Welcome back<br />
            Got a brand new track<br />
            It’s your boy Evan T<br />
            Better get up and clap<br />
            <br />
            I’m a middle aged man<br />
            Retirement plan<br />
            Got me workin like a jerk<br />
            Cause life’s a pimp hand<br />
            <br />
            Got that savoir faire<br />
            Salt and pepper hair<br />
            Kickin dope rhymes<br />
            In my favorite chair<br />
            <br />
            Yo the future looks bright<br />
            When I walk into the light<br />
            Reaper got me creepin<br />
            Like a panther in the night<br />
            <br />
            Now my bucket list<br />
            Is a fuck it list<br />
            Fist full of pills<br />
            Cause my symptoms persist<br />
            <br />
            I got pain in my lumbar six<br />
            Mind always playin tricks<br />
            Shed skin from psoriasis<br />
            Wake up in the night to piss<br />
            Time can eat a bag full of dicks<br />
            <br />
            Makin hay while the sun shines<br />
            Gray fifty shades but aged like fine wine<br />
            I’ll be keepin it real<br />
            Until the last line<br />
          </div>
        </article>
      </li>

      {/* The One - A software engineer goes hard */}
      <li>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span>The One - A software engineer goes hard</span>
          <a
            href="https://open.spotify.com/track/2lkavA27Lflz9bRWWcAmaK?si=f6c10b5a354b483c"
            class="transition-colors hover:text-primary hover:drop-shadow-[0_0_6px_var(--color-primary)]"
            aria-label="Listen to The One on Spotify"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="size-5 fill-current" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d={siSpotify.path}></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://music.apple.com/us/song/the-one/1675247385"
            class="transition-colors hover:text-primary hover:drop-shadow-[0_0_6px_var(--color-primary)]"
            aria-label="Listen to The One on Apple Music"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="size-5 fill-current" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d={siApplemusic.path}></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://music.youtube.com/watch?v=j2tLr-SthEA&si=CPuRN6kxcCcgB-Ov"
            class="transition-colors hover:text-primary hover:drop-shadow-[0_0_6px_var(--color-primary)]"
            aria-label="Listen to The One on YouTube Music"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="size-5 fill-current" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d={siYoutubemusic.path}></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </h2>
        <article class="flex flex-col md:flex-row! gap-4 pt-4">
          <figure class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
            <Image
              loading="eager"
              class="w-full h-94 aspect-square object-cover rounded-xl border"
              width={800}
              height={800}
              src="/music/posters/the_one.png"
              alt="Matrix inspired poster for the song The One."
            />
            <audio controls preload="metadata" class="w-full">
              <source src="/music/songs/the_one.mp3" type="audio/mpeg" />
            </audio>
            Soundscape by CRITICAL BASS THEORY
          </figure>

          <div
            class="flex flex-col
              md:max-w-xl md:max-h-120! max-h-56
              rounded-xl border bg-muted
              p-4
              scrollbar-visible"
          >
            My mind is a gold mine<br />
            My clock set to go time<br />
            Hyperboles over these beats<br />
            I got dope rhymes<br />
            <br />
            I try to be prolific<br />
            A gift to the gifted<br />
            Words so absurd<br />
            Your world gets flipded<br />
            <br />
            I live that nerd life<br />
            Balance that work life<br />
            Droppin shit from on high while I fly<br />
            Cause I’m bird-like<br />
            <br />
            Play by my own rules<br />
            But live by a code<br />
            Writing software. Writing rhymes<br />
            Every line so bold<br />
            <br />
            Execution like a textbook<br />
            Mouth like a check book<br />
            Verses hard as cash<br />
            Unexpected like a left hook<br />
            <br />
            Word to the word play<br />
            Nerd is my surname<br />
            Respect to the glasses<br />
            Yes sir, I got nerd game<br />
            <br />
            Rhythm like an algorithm<br />
            Code so clean<br />
            Hack into the system<br />
            The world is my machine<br />
            Rockin this shit like the matrix, son!<br />
            <br />
            Break through the fakeness<br />
            Evan T is The One<br />
          </div>
        </article>
      </li>

      {/* The Basics - A cultural subordination */}
      <li>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span>The Basics - A cultural subordination</span>
          <a
            href="https://open.spotify.com/track/126yYEfOGDXveotijat79V?si=20891010d5004cdf"
            class="transition-colors hover:text-primary hover:drop-shadow-[0_0_6px_var(--color-primary)]"
            aria-label="Listen to The Basics on Spotify"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="size-5 fill-current" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d={siSpotify.path}></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://music.apple.com/us/song/the-basics/1675248316"
            class="transition-colors hover:text-primary hover:drop-shadow-[0_0_6px_var(--color-primary)]"
            aria-label="Listen to The Basics on Apple Music"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="size-5 fill-current" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d={siApplemusic.path}></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://music.youtube.com/watch?v=nt00TTRV2F8&si=yztFfYSTdZO9pOaQ"
            class="transition-colors hover:text-primary hover:drop-shadow-[0_0_6px_var(--color-primary)]"
            aria-label="Listen to The Basics on YouTube Music"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="size-5 fill-current" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d={siYoutubemusic.path}></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </h2>
        <article class="flex flex-col md:flex-row! gap-4 pt-4">
          <figure class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
            <Image
              loading="eager"
              class="w-full h-94 aspect-square object-cover rounded-xl border"
              width={800}
              height={800}
              src="/music/posters/the_basics.png"
              alt="Truman Show inspired poster for the song The Basics."
            />
            <audio controls preload="metadata" class="w-full">
              <source src="/music/songs/the_basics.mp3" type="audio/mpeg" />
            </audio>
            Beats by The Candle Man
          </figure>

          <div
            class="flex flex-col
              md:max-w-xl md:max-h-120! max-h-56
              rounded-xl border bg-muted
              p-4
              scrollbar-visible"
          >
            Not gonna lie, I’m a basic guy<br />
            When I get a latte, It’s pumpkin spice<br />
            You can try to judge me, I won’t live a lie<br />
            Yes I’m a yuppie, I work 9 to 5<br />
            <br />
            Made this song on my Mac Book Pro<br />
            Shop on amazon with my new iPhone<br />
            Watch NBA on my Apple TV<br />
            Wake up every day with an average physique<br />
            <br />
            Face it. I’m basic<br />
            I claim it. Embrace it<br />
            <br />
            Haters gonna hate it, they can keep it real<br />
            I prefer to fake it and that’s the deal<br />
            Used to give a shit, now I don’t give a fuck<br />
            If that ain’t legit, then I’m shit out of luck<br />
            <br />
            Got no game and I get no play<br />
            Shop at the gap, wear slacks all day<br />
            Watch what I say, and I stay in my lane<br />
            Don’t want any trouble, I won’t complain<br />
            <br />
            Face it. It’s basic<br />
            That’s how I play it<br />
            <br />
            Careful what you say if you wanna stay A-list<br />
            Join every cause or they’ll call you a racist<br />
            Cancel culture won, this is what replaced it<br />
            Why make art, when the world wants hatred<br />
            <br />
            If you talk shit, I’ll change the subject<br />
            Avoid conflict cuz I gotta say fuck it<br />
            Now I gotta end it, Evan T on blast<br />
            Someone got offended, getting shut down fast<br />
            <br />
            Face it. Stay basic<br />
            Complacent is safest<br />
          </div>
        </article>
      </li>

      {/* Tiger Beat - Raw ambition meets a silky groove */}
      <li>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span>Tiger Beat - Raw ambition meets a silky groove</span>
          <a
            href="https://open.spotify.com/track/6VmZPxlRPKH5pFLY28Ptgf?si=e0b77ff4c64b4f81"
            class="transition-colors hover:text-primary hover:drop-shadow-[0_0_6px_var(--color-primary)]"
            aria-label="Listen to Tiger Beat on Spotify"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="size-5 fill-current" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d={siSpotify.path}></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://music.apple.com/us/song/tiger-beat/1675247382"
            class="transition-colors hover:text-primary hover:drop-shadow-[0_0_6px_var(--color-primary)]"
            aria-label="Listen to Tiger Beat on Apple Music"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="size-5 fill-current" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d={siApplemusic.path}></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://music.youtube.com/watch?v=YBcS0qMQzAo&si=AFGPW1Vin0-IJhHl"
            class="transition-colors hover:text-primary hover:drop-shadow-[0_0_6px_var(--color-primary)]"
            aria-label="Listen to Tiger Beat on YouTube Music"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="size-5 fill-current" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d={siYoutubemusic.path}></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </h2>
        <article class="flex flex-col md:flex-row! gap-4 pt-4">
          <figure class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
            <Image
              loading="eager"
              class="w-full h-94 aspect-square object-cover rounded-xl border"
              width={800}
              height={800}
              src="/music/posters/tiger_beat.png"
              alt="Crouching Tiger inspired poster for the song Tiger Beat."
            />
            <audio controls preload="metadata" class="w-full">
              <source src="/music/songs/tiger_beat.mp3" type="audio/mpeg" />
            </audio>
            Sampling by Ox Dx
          </figure>

          <div
            class="flex flex-col
              md:max-w-xl md:max-h-120! max-h-56
              rounded-xl border bg-muted
              p-4
              scrollbar-visible"
          >
            I’m a hard act follow<br />
            A hard pill to swallow<br />
            Like the red one from the matrix<br />
            I’m so real it’s hard to take this<br />
            Back in effect with my brother Mike Z<br />
            Got no respect for the powers that be<br />
            <br />
            Climb to the top of every single playlist<br />
            Not gonna stop til I’m known as the greatest<br />
            Recognize the game and the voice behind it<br />
            I’m the people choice. Evan T redefined it<br />
            <br />
            Fearless, cuz stereotypes don’t faze me<br />
            An Asian and a Jew makin Hip Hop so tasty<br />
            Yes I have a tiger mom. Yes my blood is tiger balm<br />
            I’m a class act and class is in session<br />
            So grab a notepad cuz here’s a free lesson<br />
            <br />
            Brooklyn to the Bay from the East to the West<br />
            Always on point cuz we strive to impress<br />
            Rock the microphone when we put it to the test<br />
            So you better use protection cuz you’re fuckin with the best<br />
          </div>
        </article>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</Layout>
